  m_text: "Your goal is to collect a hand in which your cards sum to a value as close
    to 21 without going over.\n\n(J, Q, K are all considered 10s, A can be worth
    1 or 11)\n\n1. Place your bet before the deal. If you win, you will get double
    your bet (e.g. if you bet 10, you will recieve 20).\n\n2. The dealer will deal
    two cards to everyone at the table. \n\n3. You will be given the choice to \"hit\"
    or \"stand\". Click \"hit\" to be dealt another card. Click \"stand\" to keep
    your current hand. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9f9aa37987194f64ebeee01dad058a5d, type: 2}
